Life. The universe that senses itself.
The universe that becomes capable of understand itself, and by doing so separating into subject and object.
I am not simply a piece of the universe. I can act upon it.
And so can all forms of life that inhabit it.
I am subject, we are subject. 
But we can forget about it. We can become object. We can turn others into objects. 
I must not forget about it.
I am subject, we are subject.
